16 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
17 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a joint
18 resolution to approve or disapprove administrative rules.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
20 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
21 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves all proposed
22 permanent rules of the Oklahoma Department of Aerospace and
23 Aeronautics filed on or before February 1, 2026.
